<%= email_greeting(@user) %>,

a member profile was reported. Profile reports are urgent: a second
independent report freezes the whole profile.

  Profile:      @<%= @owner_slug %> (<%= @url %><%= @owner_slug %>)
  Reported as:  <%= @category_label %>
  Reports:      <%= @report_count %><%= if @note do %>
  Reporter's note: <%= @note %><% end %>

Please review the case:

<%= @url %>admin/moderation/<%= @case_id %>

<%= render "_signature_en.text" %>

<%= render "_footer.text" %>
